<h1 class="sectionedit1" id="xdsl_digital_subscriber_line">xDSL (Digital subscriber line)</h1>
<div class="level1">
<div class="table sectionedit2"><table class="inline">
	<tr class="row0">
		<td class="col0" rowspan="2"> </td><td class="col1"> <strong><code>Note</code></strong>: This page is for <strong>hardware and driver</strong>; for help configuring your Internet connection, please see <a href="../howto/internet.connection" class="wikilink1" title="doc:howto:internet.connection">Configuration of the Internet connection</a> </td>
	</tr>
	<tr class="row1">
		<td class="col0"> See the other <a href="internet.access.technologies" class="wikilink1" title="doc:hardware:internet.access.technologies">internet.access.technologies</a>. </td>
	</tr>
</table></div>

</div>

<h2 class="sectionedit3" id="overview">Overview</h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
There are at least three companies with <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital subscriber line" class="interwiki iw_wp" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital subscriber line">xDSL</a>-Solutions:
</p>
